

**Matsh am hi g Jesus amai matsh am haꞌi e hohont **

1 Am gohk d i tash amjed, tsh am haꞌi wo e hohont Cana kihhim t am. Ihda Cana o am Galilee chekchani ch ed. K am haꞌichug g Jesus jeꞌe. 2 Kumd ahchim ab i t-wai. Chd am hihi g Jesus wehm k am haꞌichug. Kumd am hahawa hab juh g gegosig. 3 D wabshaba am i huh g nawait. D g Jesus jeꞌe ab wui hab kaij, “Huh at g ha-nawait.” 

4 D hab kaij g Jesus, “Pi o ab hu haꞌichu ni-him heg amjed. Pi at koi chum e ai mant am wo i ni-maskogi.” 

5 D wabshaba g jeꞌej hab ha ahg g pion, “Am g hab wo juhni matp haschu wo i em-ahgi mamt am hab wo juh.” 

6 K eda d t-himdag ahchim Tutuligo mach muꞌi haꞌichu has masma wapkon. D g hohodai hahaꞌa chuhdp am dadha mamt ab wo chum waꞌig k am hab wo junihid g t-himdag. D idam hahaꞌa hemako am hu i waikko wehst-mahm walohn shuhdagi am wo e toa. 

7 D hab kaij g Jesus am ha wui g pion, “Am g wo i ha shuhshud g shuhdagikaj.” 

D wa woho am si i ha shuhshud. 

8 D hab hahawa ep ha ahg, “Am g wo wassibi k wo mah hegai mo nuhkud g e-hohontam piast.” 

D wa woho hab e juh k am i wassibi k ged hu ha mah. 9 D ab jeh mo d si s-kehg nawait k eda pi mahch mas hebai waꞌi. Hegam o hi wa s-mahch pion mat hebai waꞌi. 10 D am i cheh g ha-hohntam am i jehk g nawait k hab kaij ab wui, “Shaꞌi s-ap ab kahk ihda nawait. Haꞌi at an hi wo wa i ha wassibi g s-kehg nawait ga hu i wehpeg k wabsh g pi kehg nawait wo ha wassibi im hu i oidch. Kuptki eda ahpi im hu i oidch g si s-kehg nawait ha wassibi.” 

11 Neh, k id d si wehpeg s-hasig haꞌichu hab junij g Jesus. D am mahsko wua g e-gewkdag. Kuchd ab si s-wohochud mo woho d Jiosh si Kehsha. 

12 D am hahawa hab i e ah g Jesus matt am wo hihi Capernaum kihhim wui. D g jeꞌej ch wepngaj ep t-oi. Ch am haꞌichugkahim heꞌekia tash. 

**Matsh gam hu hih g Jesus geꞌe cheopi wui **

*An g neid g Matthew 21:12-13; Mark 11:15-17; Luke 19:45-46 *

13 Wehs ahid ab o am e wushshad Jerusalem t am matsh wa g Jiosh ha doꞌibia g t‑shohshon. Kud am i e ai. Kuchd gam hu hihim 14 k ged hu dada geꞌe cheopi t am. D eda am haꞌi ha gagda g haiwani ch kahwal ch hohohi ch am haꞌi kammialt g lial heg wehhejed. 15 Kud si pi hohhoꞌi g Jesus mo id am hab e wua geꞌe cheopi t am k hekaj hema gewikudt g wijinakaj k gam hu wehs si ha shahmud g haiwani ch kahwal k am gai ha shul g ha‑mimsa hegam mo g lial kammialt k gam hu si gantad g ha‑lialiga 16 k hab ha ahg hegam mo g hohohi ha gagda mat gam hu wo i ha wuwhas hab kaijch, “Pi g hab wo shaꞌi juhni g ni‑ohg kih mat d wabsh wo haꞌichu gagdakudk.” 

17 Kuchd am hahawa i chegito mo g Jiosh heki oꞌohana hab chuꞌig: 

Jiosh si Kehsha at ab wo si has elidad g geꞌe cheopi. *Psalm 69:9 * 

18 D ab si chehmo g hahaꞌichu k hab ahg, “Shahchu ap ahgch hab wua ihda? Am g hig t‑chehgid g s‑hasig haꞌichu. Kutt hab wo s‑mahchk map uꞌukch g e‑gewkdag ab amjed g Jiosh.” 

19 D hab kaij g Jesus, “Pegih oig, m ant wo wa em‑chehgi g s‑hasig haꞌichu. Mt wo padch ihda mo g Jiosh am eda kih. Kunt ahni ep wo i kegch mat d wo i waik tashk.” 

20 D idam si e shoꞌoshodkad k hab kaij, “Giꞌikko gamai chuhdp \(46\) aꞌahid ab at hahawa i e nahto ihda geꞌe cheopi. Kuptp eda ahpi waik tash ab ia wo i kei.” 

21 K eda g Jesus hejel hab e ahg mat wo e muhkid k uhpam ep wo e chegito. 22 Kutt s‑chegito g neꞌokij mat hekid uhpam e chegito am e muhkidk. Neh, bo chuꞌig g Jiosh oꞌohana mat uhpam wo e chegito g Jiosh si Kehsha. Kutt hahawa s‑amichud k ab s‑wohoch. 

**S‑mahch o g Jesus g hemajkam ha‑chegitoi **

23-24 Am achd haꞌichugkahim Jerusalem t am wehs oidam g t‑shohshon ha‑doꞌibiadag wuhshda. Kud muꞌijj ab i s‑wohoch g Jesus. D wabshaba pi am hu i e tashogi ha wui mas hedai wud no pi s‑mahch mo heg wabsh hekaj ab s‑wohochud mo am neid mo hab juni him g s‑hasig haꞌichu. 25 Pi o hedai ab hu hiwig g Jesus mas am wo ahgi g hemajkam ha‑chegitoi no pi heki hu s‑mahch. 

